1... Rxh2 wins a pawn and creates strong pressure on the h-file. If White plays 2. Rh1, Black has 2... Rxh1# (mate). Best defense is 2. Ke1, after which 2... Rg2 (or 2... Bxc5) gives Black a clear edge.
